{"tid":229400,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]解熊大隻兔兔成個膠神咁？(老母節鉅獻)","createTime":"2017-05-04T14:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T07:48:29.000Z","uid":69088,"like":50,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15d3053c8ad682077737c0b77e34100703d6b976","tid":229400,"uid":69088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:38:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的⋯<br />\n<br />\n細佬個女朋友 Connie 年幾前去左英國讀書<br />\n臨走前送左熊大隻 Cony 俾細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n細佬當佢如珠如寶，日日都攬住佢<br />\n攬到隻嘢都有d黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁老母見到就拎去洗衣機洗啦<br />\n點知洗甩左條尾⋯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">之後老母就好醒咁將條尾<br />\n補返落Cony個鼻到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/222751_98057ce09849f2c03350b47720886324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F222751_98057ce09849f2c03350b47720886324.jpg&h=22529a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cR4Ma03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcR4Ma03.jpg&h=dd713e81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/222831_b9aae832445c3a3ecd4519be4e10cb80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F222831_b9aae832445c3a3ecd4519be4e10cb80.jpg&h=0aa38971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/222813_3dbe7a84d64a2be6154ca10092e6fbee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F222813_3dbe7a84d64a2be6154ca10092e6fbee.jpg&h=ed057d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> -依家靚好多，唔好話俾老母知<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> -以前好啲，但都要tag佢等女朋友發現"},{"pid":"2b9771ad9db808a0203762f36dc9a3f0590457c3","tid":229400,"uid":8213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皮已正"},{"pid":"f7cfccaf65f0e0256bb11686e9737c65e89e51ec","tid":229400,"uid":81828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"成日覺得老母幫仔女縫野好溫馨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6182be8214bfa486cb9e8a7cab16920c6ec4c265","tid":229400,"uid":68407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你媽媽好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d3ff54fe5879b59acf7d7b1433fb88a39d0cb1","tid":229400,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"048776726499cec2efe4ed17208e8cae39854977","tid":229400,"uid":29724,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"膠你老母神呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869f47bdb7a6ebf7a12277d688d2e5fa2f448078","tid":229400,"uid":69088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci